import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'
import List from '.././components/Cart/List/List'
import TotalPrice from '.././components/Cart/TotalPrice/TotalPrice'
import Address from '../components/Cart/Address/Address'
import Header from '../components/Header/header'
import Footer from '../components/Footer/footer'

function Cart() {
    return (
        <>
        <Header/>
        <Box sx={{
            display:'flex',
        }}>
            <Box sx={{
                bgcolor:'red',
                width:'60%',
                height:'10rem'
            }}>
                <Address />
                <List />
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <TotalPrice />
            </Box>
        </Box>
        <Footer/>
        </>
    )
}

export default Cart
